      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend section 19 of title 3, United States Code, to allow the President to choose between possible successors in case of the event that, by reason of certain circumstances, there is neither a President nor Vice President to discharge the powers and duties of the office of President, and for other purposes.</title>
